title: Elon Musk Tries to Direct AI---Again
description: His latest startup follows a decade of being outmaneuvered in his quest to steer the development of artificial intelligence.

title: Israeli Startups Struggle to Raise Money Amid Political Turmoil, Global Downturn
description: Companies at the major tech hub saw a 70% drop in funding in the first quarter of 2023 compared with a year prior and underperformed the worldwide average. The coming quarters should give a clearer picture of the impact of a contentious judicial overhaul plan.
